Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.00,1:07:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.01,1:07:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就你先来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.01,1:07:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,谁喜欢舔屁股
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.02,1:07:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,干劲十足喔
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.02,1:07:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,快舔
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.03,1:08:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,兴奋吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.03,1:08:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.04,1:08:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,舔得起劲呢
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.04,1:08:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,从下面摸肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.06,1:08:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不错喔
