Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.04,1:09:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,说啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.04,1:09:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,问你话啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.04,1:09:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.05,1:09:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.05,1:09:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,听不到说清楚点
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.05,1:09:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,肛门好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.06,1:09:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.00,1:09:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,说得好
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.00,1:09:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,看着镜头
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.00,1:09:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,说  肛门好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.00,1:09:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,肛门好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.01,1:09:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不像话
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.02,1:10:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,吃肉棒吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.02,1:10:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,随便干吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.03,1:10:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.03,1:10:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不止一根喔 这边也有
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.05,1:10:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,用手
