Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.03,1:15:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我比较厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.04,1:15:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.04,1:16:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,友情崩溃了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.04,1:16:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这么不值钱
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.05,1:16:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,继续吃
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.05,1:16:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.05,1:16:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢谁的
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.06,1:16:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.06,1:16:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,结梨吧
